    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is considered credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the declared COU. The primary validation result demonstrates agreement with FDA GCBP bench data within the CPB operating envelope, and the secondary Leverett dataset provides corroborating evidence for the hemolysis model coefficients. The assessment team accepted both validation activities as meeting Gradation 2 for Output Comparison and Relevance of Validation Activities. The decision is Accepted.",
